OL,3,CMore patients waiting longer to be
OL,4,Cdischarged from hospital
OL,6,FThe number of delayed discharges from
OL,7,Fhospital in Dumfries and Galloway has
OL,8,Fincreased by 27.8% over the year
OL,9,Fleading to October 2025, while in NHS
OL,10,FBorders the figure decreased by 44.8%,
OL,11,Faccording to a new independent report.
OL,13,FDelayed discharge is when patients are
OL,14,Fready to be discharged from hospital
OL,15,Fbut are unable to leave.
