OL,3,CMore patients waiting longer to be
OL,4,Cdischarged from hospital
OL,6,FThe reasons why can be varied and
OL,7,Fcomplex, ranging from unavailable care
OL,8,Fspaces, unsuitable living conditions
OL,9,Fat home for recovery, delayed home
OL,10,Fassessments, or not having a power of
OL,11,Fattorney in place.
OL,13,FThe figures from Audit Scotland show
OL,14,Fthat delayed discharge cost NHS
OL,15,FScotland #440m between April 2024 and
OL,16,FApril 2025.
OL,18,FIn NHS Borders, a census snapshot
OL,19,Fshowed 84 delays in October 2024,
OL,20,Fwhich reduced to 43 delays in October
OL,21,F2025.
