OL,6,FIn NHS Dumfries and Galloway, there
OL,7,Fwere 79 delays in October 2024, which
OL,8,Fincreased to 101 in October 2025,
OL,9,Fmaking the region one of the worst for
OL,10,Fdelayed discharge in Scotland.
OL,12,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway did not
OL,13,Frespond to ITV Border's requests to
OL,14,Fcomment, while NHS Borders said no-one
OL,15,Fwas available to speak.
