OL,6,FHealth Secretary Neil Gray said: "We
OL,7,Fare grateful for Audit Scotland's
OL,8,Freport and share the view that,
OL,9,Fdespite the hard work this government
OL,10,Fhas undertaken in partnership with
OL,11,FCoSLA and Health and Social Care
OL,12,FPartnerships, more must be done to
OL,13,Fensure people receive the care they
OL,14,Fneed in the right place, at the right
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,F"We agree that nationally consistent
OL,18,Fperformance information is critically
OL,19,Fimportant for improving outcomes.
