OL,6,F"Local systems have been working hard
OL,7,Fto reduce delays and deliver on the
OL,8,Fcommitments set out in our Operational
OL,9,FImprovement Plan, supported by
OL,10,Finvestment of over #220 million to
OL,11,Fimprove patient flow, enhance capacity
OL,12,Fand remove blockages keeping patients
OL,13,Fin hospital longer than necessary.
OL,14,FThis winter, that includes up to #20
OL,15,Fmillion to fund increased social care
OL,16,Fand reduce pressure on the hospital
OL,17,Ffront door.
